  "engines": [
    "Obrix"
  ],
  "description": "gestureType=3 (the FLASH gesture mode) with flashTrigger=0.8 — the FLASH feature activated at high intensity. Every note triggers a structural event: the sound reconfigures itself percussively before settling. Square + Saw (both aggressive, even harmonics from Saw, odd from Square) through proc1=HP (stripping lows for a bright percussive crack), then proc2=LP as envelope shaper. ampAttack 0.002s for brick-fast transients. VelEnv→amp makes velocity a structural force: soft hits build, hard hits detonate.",
